### 2025-12-14 — Documentation Pays Off 💡

**Context:** Building the _meta.notes Personal section

**Learning:** Taking time to create templates and README files upfront feels slow but dramatically accelerates future work. The investment in structure pays dividends every time you use it.

**Application:**
- Always create a README when making a new folder
- Templates are worth 10x the time to create them
- Future-me will thank present-me for documentation

**Related:** [[Personal/README]]

