### 2025-12-14 — Obsidian Dataview Power 🔧

**Context:** Creating Project Velocity dashboard

**Learning:** DataviewJS can do almost anything, but simple TABLE queries cover 80% of use cases. Start simple, upgrade to JS only when needed.

**Technique:**
```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link as "Note",
  dateformat(file.mtime, "yyyy-MM-dd") as "Updated"
FROM "folder"
SORT file.mtime DESC
LIMIT 10
```

**Related:** [[Snippets/Dataview Query Library]], [[Dashboards/Project Velocity]]

